      "date": "2012-10-27 23:44:47.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.8/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/55d1f35c-208e-11e2-9023-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
